==Geography== * State – [[Pernambuco]] * Region – [[Zona da Mata (coastal)|Zona da mata Pernambucana]] * Boundaries – [[Passira]] ('''N'''); [[Primavera, Pernambuco|Primavera]] ('''S'''); [[Gravatá]] and [[Chã Grande]] ('''W'''); [[Vitória de Santo Antão]] ('''E''') * Area – 207.66&nbsp;km<sup>2</sup> * Elevation – 208 m * Hidrography – [[Ipojuca River|Ipojuca]] and [[Capibaribe River]] rivers * Vegetation – [[Subperenifólia]] forest * Clima – Hot tropical and humid * Annual average temperature – 23.8 c * Distance to [[Recife]] – 60&nbsp;km
==Economy== The main economic activities in Pombos are based in commerce and [[agribusiness]], especially [[sugarcane]], [[pineapple]]s, [[manioc]], [[lemon]]s and livestock such as [[cattle]] and [[goat]]s.
